      "@id": "https://data.datatourisme.fr/e1665d4a-d724-36b0-8797-b310f2513d64",
      "dc:description": {
        "de": [
          "Treffen Sie die besten Segler auf einer außergewöhnlichen Wasserfläche. Parallel zu den Rennen findet ein kostenloses und für alle zugängliches Dorf mit Konferenzen, Ausstellungen, Verkostungen und Ständen rund um die marine Biodiversität und die Umwelt statt. Eine Woche, in der sich sportliche Leistung und umweltbewusstes Engagement miteinander verbinden. Infos und Anmeldung auf der Website: yccarnac.com"
        ],
        "en": [
          "The Yacht Club de Carnac will host the ACO Musto Skiff World Championship 2026 from 6 to 12 June 2026, marking the return of this prestigious international regatta to Carnac, ten years after the 2016 edition. The event will bring together the world’s top sailors in the class on one of Europe’s most renowned sailing venues.\n\nThe schedule will include a pre-worlds regatta on 7 June, followed by five days of World Championship racing from 8 to 12 June, with up to 14 races planned. A full social programme will also be offered at the club, including social evenings and a gala dinner for competitors.\n\nThe championship is organised with the support of title sponsor ACO, a global leader in drainage technology, alongside Musto and boat builder Ovington Boats. The class continues its commitment to accessibility with a 50% entry fee reduction for youth sailors (25 years old and under), as well as dedicated prizes for youth, female sailors and competitors using the smaller Mainsail X.\n\n The Notice of Race (NOR) and online entry are available on the Yacht Club de Carnac website:\nhttps://yccarnac.ouiresa.fr/#/?keyword=MUSTO"
        ],
        "it": [
          "Incontrare i migliori velisti in uno specchio d'acqua eccezionale. Oltre alle regate, un villaggio gratuito aperto a tutti offrirà conferenze, mostre, degustazioni e stand sulla biodiversità marina e l'ambiente. Una settimana che unisce le prestazioni sportive all'impegno per l'eco-responsabilità. Informazioni e iscrizioni su: yccarnac.com"
        ],
        "fr": [
          "Retrouvez les meilleurs marins sur un plan d’eau d’exception. En parallèle des courses, un village gratuit et ouvert à tous proposera conférences, expositions, dégustations et stands autour de la biodiversité marine et de l’environnement. Une semaine mêlant performance sportive et engagement éco-responsable. Infos et inscriptions sur le site : yccarnac.com"
        ],
        "nl": [
          "Ontmoet de beste zeilers op een uitzonderlijk stuk water. Naast de races is er een gratis toegankelijk dorp met conferenties, tentoonstellingen, proeverijen en stands over mariene biodiversiteit en het milieu. Een week die sportieve prestaties combineert met een inzet voor eco-verantwoordelijkheid. Informatie en registratie op: yccarnac.com"
        ],
        "es": [
          "Conozca a los mejores regatistas en un tramo de agua excepcional. Junto a las regatas, un village gratuito y abierto a todos ofrecerá conferencias, exposiciones, degustaciones y stands sobre biodiversidad marina y medio ambiente. Una semana que combina rendimiento deportivo y compromiso con la ecorresponsabilidad. Información e inscripciones en: yccarnac.com"
        ]
      },
